headline: 10 Reasons to Buy and Hold This Semiconductor Stock Forever
summary: TSMC is one of the most dominant tech companies in the world.  The company is delivering strong growth and wide profit margins.  Taiwan Semiconductor Manufacturing (NYSE: TSM) is one of the most valuable companies in the world at a market cap of $1.1 trillion, but it doesn't get the same level of attention that other big tech stocks get like Nvidia or Microsoft do.

headline: 5 Considerations Ahead Of BlackBerry's Q1 Report
summary: BlackBerry faces macro headwinds and weak guidance, but long-term QNX growth and cost cuts support a turnaround thesis. See why BB stock is a buy.
